libkoralle is a lib for parsing (and hopefully soon also writing) data
in Resource Interchange File Format (RIFF) based formats.

Documentation about RIFF:
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Resource_Interchange_File_Format

Known users:
Import filter for Karbon (WIP, contact kossebau@kde.org)

Authors:
Friedrich W. H. Kossebau <kossebau@kde.org>
soon you?